IDFC, LIC Sign Agreement for Infrastructure Financing

-- B y   A n o o p   A g r a w a l
-- 
2011-09-17T09:21:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-17/idfc-lic-sign-agreement-for-infrastructure-financing.html
India  Infrastructure Finance Co.,
Infrastructure Development Finance Co. and Life Insurance Corp.
of India have signed an agreement to fund infrastructure
projects in the country, the government said.   Under the accord, IDFC will finance 10 percent of the debt
of a project while the other two will fund 20 percent each, the
government said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anoop Agrawal in Mumbai at 
